<h2 id="section-top">Gastrointestinal and Liver services</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=967">Pennine Acute Hospitals NHS Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">The Pennine Acute Hospitals NHS Trust<br/>0161 624 0420</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent0a72e680a4974d41a1f5cc8c9e675f5a">
</div>
<p><strong><em>Gastroenterology</em> - out-patient and day surgery services are provided on all hospital sites within the Trust with the exception of Birch Hill in Rochdale.</strong></p>
<p><strong><em>Hepatology</em> - out-patient services are only available at North Manchester General.  In patient services are available at Fairfield General and North Manchester.</strong></p></div>
</div>
</div>
